          "content": "## Setup (read me)\n1) Open the Gmail node and connect credentials.\n2) Set the **To** field to your email or team list.\n3) Save this workflow, then in each target workflow go to **Options ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Error workflow** and select this.\n\n### About the payload\nThis uses Error Trigger fields:\n- `{{$json[\"workflow\"][\"name\"]}}` / `{{$json[\"workflow\"][\"id\"]}}`\n- `{{$json[\"execution\"][\"id\"] || \"N/A\"}}`\n- `{{$json[\"execution\"][\"url\"] || \"N/A\"}}`\n- `{{$json[\"execution\"][\"lastNodeExecuted\"] || \"N/A\"}}`\n- `{{$json[\"execution\"][\"error\"][\"message\"]}}`\n\nFor trigger-time failures, execution fields may be missing‚Äîemail still sends with fallbacks."
